WEBVTT

00:00:15.483 --> 00:00:16.831
Što je algoritam?

00:00:16.831 --> 00:00:17.662
U informatici,

00:00:17.662 --> 00:00:19.416
algoritam je skup uputa

00:00:19.416 --> 00:00:22.105
za rješavanje nekog problema,
korak-po-korak.

00:00:22.105 --> 00:00:24.377
U pravilu, algoritme izvršavaju računala,

00:00:24.377 --> 00:00:26.544
ali i mi ljudi imamo algoritme.

00:00:26.544 --> 00:00:28.397
Na primjer, kako biste izbrojali

00:00:28.397 --> 00:00:30.217
broj ljudi u prostoriji?